game.name: Wheely 3
game.description:
Wheely is back with more adventurous and funny journey in the third sequel of this highly addictive and popular Wheely game series! The wheels of wifey Jolie have been spoiled and now this cute Beetle has decided to arrange them for his beloved one. However, it is not possible at all without your precious helping hands. So, are you ready to help your cute friend once again? Join Wheely 3 and get ready to find out a new pair of wheels for his lovely wifey! 

The job looks easy, but includes making some quick decisions to achieve the goal in this brand new adventure game. Your best friend needs to get ready to face off various obstacles since the street is full of life threatening dangers. Find out the clues and unravel the logic-based puzzles to progress through each of the fantastic levels. Make the best use of available tools and determine quickly how to reach the red flag to complete each level successfully. 

You can click on Wheely to move or stop during the gameplay in this free online adventure game. Use the mouse again to drag items and apply them when required. Let your wits and curiosity work for you to solve the logical based puzzles and brain teasers in this cool point and click adventure game! This cool kids game can be played on both desktop and mobile browser. Play this popular HTML5 game to improve your brain power! Visit our free online game website right away to find out some more tricky and exciting platform games!
